#smallest among three number
x = float(input("enter the first number"))
y = float(input("enter  the second number"))
z = float(input("enter  the third number"))

#logic started

if (x <= y) and (x <=z):
    s = x
elif (y <= x) and (y <= z):
      s = y
else :
    s =z
    
#display
print("the smallest of three number is:",s)    
output:
enter the first number 21
enter  the second number 1987
enter  the third number  1995
the smallest of three number is: 21.0
